- You will stand fast!
- He'll be dead before you get to him!

235
00:17:55,268 --> 00:17:58,362
- The air hose!
- Stand off! I will take you
to the captain's mast,

236
00:17:58,438 --> 00:18:01,305
and you will lose if you touch
that water, do you hear me?

237
00:18:01,374 --> 00:18:03,501
Yes, sir!

238
00:18:06,746 --> 00:18:08,839
Goddamn it!

239
00:18:28,368 --> 00:18:33,465
Master Chief Sunday,
you've sustained a serious embolism.

240
00:18:33,540 --> 00:18:37,909
- Embolism?
- Both lobes of the lungs
were severely scarred.

241
00:18:37,978 --> 00:18:40,242
Can't cheat the laws of nature
forever, can you, Doc?

242
00:18:40,313 --> 00:18:43,248
I'm afraid the condition's
totally inoperable.

243
00:18:43,316 --> 00:18:45,876
[ Sighs ]
Ain't that a bitch?

244
00:18:49,222 --> 00:18:52,658
So what happens next time I go diving?
I start taking on bottom pressure?

245
00:18:52,726 --> 00:18:56,093
Any increased pressure at all
will kill you, instantly.

246
00:18:56,162 --> 00:19:00,724
Kill me. Goddamn, for a minute there
I thought this was serious.

247
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:03,325
- If you could keep your voice down.
- Hell, no.

248
00:19:03,403 --> 00:19:05,701
Goddamn,
I feel like singin', man.

249
00:19:05,772 --> 00:19:09,401
- Ah, fuck!
- Where are you going?

250
00:19:09,476 --> 00:19:13,003
Get me a drink. Celebrate.
You had me going.
I thought I couldn't go diving no more.

251
00:19:13,079 --> 00:19:16,048
- Chief Sunday,
you're scaring the patients.
- How about me?

252
00:19:16,116 --> 00:19:20,177
Goddamn. Hey, I got an idea.
Maybe you can use me around here.

253
00:19:20,253 --> 00:19:23,245
Hell, I'm lookin'
to make a career move.

254
00:19:23,323 --> 00:19:27,020
Maybe, maybe you can get
someone to change the bed pans!

255
00:19:27,093 --> 00:19:30,927
- Change the fuckin' bed pans!
- [Orderly]Chief!

256
00:19:30,997 --> 00:19:33,727
- Change the fuckin' bed pans!
Hey! Hey!
- Hey!

257
00:19:33,800 --> 00:19:38,464
- [ Screams ]
- [ Indistinct Shouting ]

258
00:19:38,538 --> 00:19:42,372
Master Chief Sunday, given
your current physical condition...

259
00:19:42,442 --> 00:19:46,708
and the far graver issue...

260
00:19:46,780 --> 00:19:48,941
- of your recent acts of misconduct,
- [Laughter]

261
00:19:49,015 --> 00:19:52,041
you will be medically
disqualified from diving,

262
00:19:52,118 --> 00:19:54,643
fined one-half month's pay
for three months...

263
00:19:54,721 --> 00:19:56,985
and reassigned
toa training position,

264
00:19:57,057 --> 00:19:59,787
where it is
my greatest wish...

265
00:19:59,859 --> 00:20:03,158
that you will embrace
a new found respect for authority.

266
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:09,134
This hearing is concluded.

267
00:20:09,202 --> 00:20:11,170
[Gavel Raps]

268
00:20:43,036 --> 00:20:46,699
- That's what I want to be, sir.
- A Navy Master Diver?

269
00:20:46,773 --> 00:20:50,038
- Yes, sir.
- Last week, you were a cook.

270
00:20:50,110 --> 00:20:54,774
- Well, the man I just saw--
- The man you saw is a Master Chief.

271
00:20:54,848 --> 00:20:57,681
That's the highest rank an enlisted man
can achieve in the Navy.

272
00:20:57,751 --> 00:21:01,346
A lot of good men spend a career
trying to get there and fail.

273
00:21:01,421 --> 00:21:04,015
Besides,

274
00:21:04,090 --> 00:21:06,615
they are not gonna take
a colored at diving school.

275
00:21:06,693 --> 00:21:11,187
- It's as simple as that.
- What if you were to give me
a personal recommendation, sir?

276
00:21:11,264 --> 00:21:16,201
[ Chuckles ] I just made you
a deck seaman three days ago.

277
00:21:16,269 --> 00:21:19,067
What else do I owe you?

278
00:21:19,139 --> 00:21:23,576
The way I see it,
I owe you, sir.

279
00:21:31,117 --> 00:21:34,382
I'll endorse your request,
[ Chuckles ]

280
00:21:34,454 --> 00:21:36,888
but it ain't gonna work.

281
00:22:12,342 --> 00:22:14,105
Wait outside.

282
00:22:22,085 --> 00:22:27,523
